 \"to\": 371}, {\"ngram\": \"Europe\", \"from\": 375, \"to\": 381}, {\"ngram\": \"a budget carrier\", \"from\": 389, \"to\": 405}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Flying with a legacy airline, you might have paid upwards of $3500, but in 2024, it's a turnaround.\", \"from\": 424, \"to\": 523, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a legacy airline\", \"from\": 436, \"to\": 452}, {\"ngram\": \"a turnaround\", \"from\": 510, \"to\": 522}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Those same legacy carriers have shaved about $1000 off their Europe fares, but the real bargains are coming from the Asian carriers, with China Eastern Airlines in the spotlight.\", \"from\": 525, \"to\": 703, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 642, \"end\": 647, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asia\", \"score\": 0.9998687420878684, \"rank\": 0.00012274780276610582, \"text\": \"Asian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asia\"}, {\"begin\": 663, \"end\": 685, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Eastern_Airlines\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"China Eastern Airlines\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q46970\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Eastern_Airlines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Eastern_Airlines\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Those same legacy carriers\", \"from\": 525, \"to\": 551}, {\"ngram\": \"their Europe fares\", \"from\": 580, \"to\": 598}, {\"ngram\": \"the real bargains\", \"from\": 604, \"to\": 621}, {\"ngram\": \"the spotlight\", \"from\": 689, \"to\": 702}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Right now, you can snap up an airfare to Paris to coincide with the summer Olympic Games, leaving Australia in mid-July and returning towards the end of August, for under $1500.\", \"from\": 705, \"to\": 882, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 746, \"end\": 751, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999949978, \"rank\": 5.188672964867092