 on international flights into and out of Australia.\", \"from\": 2850, \"to\": 3089, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3079, \"end\": 3088, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9999999991600816, \"rank\": 6.774885931809602e-10, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"February\", \"from\": 2853, \"to\": 2861}, {\"ngram\": \"figures\", \"from\": 2900, \"to\": 2907}, {\"ngram\": \"the Bureau\", \"from\": 2927, \"to\": 2937}, {\"ngram\": \"Infrastructure and Transport Research Economics\", \"from\": 2941, \"to\": 2988}, {\"ngram\": \"BITRE\", \"from\": 2990, \"to\": 2995}, {\"ngram\": \"4.17 million seats\", \"from\": 3009, \"to\": 3027}, {\"ngram\": \"international flights\", \"from\": 3041, \"to\": 3062}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's a 35 per cent increase on the number of seats available for the same month in 2023.\", \"from\": 3090, \"to\": 3180, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a 35 per cent increase\", \"from\": 3097, \"to\": 3119}, {\"ngram\": \"the number\", \"from\": 3123, \"to\": 3133}, {\"ngram\": \"seats\", \"from\": 3137, \"to\": 3142}, {\"ngram\": \"the same month\", \"from\": 3157, \"to\": 3171}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One of the airlines that has increased seat availability the most over that period is China Eastern.\", \"from\": 3182, \"to\": 3282, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3268, \"end\": 3273, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999112259445521, \"rank\": 7.366470706783106e-05, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the airlines\", \"from\": 3189, \"to\": 3201}, {\"ngram\": \"seat availability\", \"from\": 3221, \"to\": 3238}, {\"ngram\": \"that period\", \"from\": 3253, \"to\": 3264}]}, {\"sentenc